# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:41
translate spanish hwb_s22b_d08a6eb2:

    # "Once we’re quiet, the awkwardness sets in again. Where I don’t know if I should be saying something to fill the silence or if I should leave it be."
    "Una vez que nos quedamos en silencio, la incomodidad vuelve a instalarse. Donde no sé si debería decir algo para llenar el silencio o si debería dejarlo así."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:43
translate spanish hwb_s22b_540806ef:

    # "Is she thinking the same thing? Is she also worried?"
    "¿Estará pensando lo mismo? ¿También estará preocupada?"

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:45
translate spanish hwb_s22b_0e3859e8:

    # "I sneak glance after worried glance down, but I can’t see her face."
    "Lanzo miradas furtivas y preocupadas hacia abajo, pero no puedo ver su rostro."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:47
translate spanish hwb_s22b_9c1407f8:

    # "Her hands wander around like she doesn’t know what to do. She touches her face. Then scratches her leg. Picks at a fold in her shirt. Pops her knuckles."
    "Sus manos vagan como si no supiera qué hacer. Se toca la cara. Luego se rasca la pierna. Juega con un pliegue de su camisa. Se cruje los nudillos."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:49
translate spanish hwb_s22b_fe040ffe:

    # "So she is nervous."
    "Así que está nerviosa."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:53
translate spanish hwb_s22b_15865dfa:

    # Amber "Hey."
    Amber "Эй."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:55
translate spanish hwb_s22b_8da095d5:

    # "The top of her head bumps my chin as she flinches."
    "La parte superior de su cabeza choca contra mi barbilla cuando se estremece."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:57
translate spanish hwb_s22b_32d7002e:

    # Marina "Hey."
    Marina "Эй."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:61
translate spanish hwb_s22b_d8e6dd94:

    # Amber "You good?"
    Amber "Ты в порядке?"

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:63
translate spanish hwb_s22b_07cc638e:

    # Marina "Yeah."
    Marina "Ага."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:67
translate spanish hwb_s22b_347d8d5a:

    # Amber "You don’t seem good."
    Amber "А со стороны так не кажется."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:71
translate spanish hwb_s22b_6b09171e:

    # Marina "No I am! Sorry. I’m just…"
    Marina "Нет-нет, я в порядке! Прости. Я просто…"

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:73
translate spanish hwb_s22b_576d52b3:

    # "Rather than hurry her along like I sometimes do, I wait for her to find the words."
    "En lugar de apresurarla como a veces hago, espero a que encuentre las palabras."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:77
translate spanish hwb_s22b_f2c1fa27:

    # Marina "Just worried I guess."
    Marina "Наверное, я просто переживаю."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:81
translate spanish hwb_s22b_a9132c4e:

    # Marina "I’ve um… I know you have, but I’ve never had a girlfriend before."
    Marina "Я… хм… Я знаю, что у тебя до этого была девушка, а для меня это все впервые."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:83
translate spanish hwb_s22b_c25e1dbc:

    # "I start to say something, but she hurriedly cuts me off."
    "Empiezo a decir algo, pero ella me interrumpe apresuradamente."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:87
translate spanish hwb_s22b_cc6bb5d2:

    # Marina "I don’t mean it like that! Well I do, but I’ve also never had a boyfriend before. Not a real one, anyway."
    Marina "Я не то имела в виду! Ну то есть то, но.. в общем у меня и парня то не было. По крайней мере, по-настоящему."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:91
translate spanish hwb_s22b_6ce607bd:

    # Amber "You had a fake boyfriend though?"
    Amber "Но ненастоящие были?"

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:95
translate spanish hwb_s22b_5831bba7:

    # Marina "Barely. Like in middle school, there was this guy who asked if I’d be his girlfriend, and I said okay. But then the next day he said his mom told him he wasn’t allowed to have a girlfriend, so we broke up."
    Marina "Вроде того. Это было в средней школе. Один паренек спросил, буду ли я его девушкой и я сказала да. А на следующий день он сказал мне, что его мама запретила ему встречаться с девушками, так что мы расстались."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:99
translate spanish hwb_s22b_3d7b63ff:

    # Amber "Sounds brutal."
    Amber "Звучит жестоко."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:103
translate spanish hwb_s22b_f8d6e6bf:

    # Marina "Right?"
    Marina "Правда?"

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:107
translate spanish hwb_s22b_9c927c36:

    # Marina "And then junior year of high school, I kind of dated this guy for like, a month. But I didn’t really like him. My friends just wanted me to."
    Marina "А потом, в первый год в старшей школе я встречалась с парнем около месяца. Но мне он не особо нравился, просто мои друзья настояли, что я должна с ним встречаться."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:111
translate spanish hwb_s22b_9a03cfdd:

    # Amber "That’s screwed up."
    Amber "Это какая-то хрень."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:115
translate spanish hwb_s22b_f4b673fb:

    # Marina "I dunno, not really. They weren’t trying to be mean or anything. And he wasn’t a bad person. He was just… boring."
    Marina "Не знаю... не совсем. Они это делали не со зла, а он был совсем неплохим человеком. Просто он был… унылый."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:119
translate spanish hwb_s22b_7349a251:

    # Marina "Like for our first ‘date’ we went to dinner and a movie. But dinner was just fast food and he spilled ketchup all over himself."
    Marina "Например, на нашем первом “свидании” мы собирались сходить пообедать и в кино. Но обед был обычным походом в фаст-фуд,  где он весь облился кетчупом."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:121
translate spanish hwb_s22b_aad39e2b:

    # Marina "And I don’t even remember what movie we saw. He put his arm on the back of my chair and I thought he was trying to put his arm around me so I kind of got closer but nope, he just kept it up there."
    Marina "И я даже не помню на какой фильм мы ходили. Он положил руку на спинку моего кресла, а я думала, что он хочет меня обнять, поэтому придвинулась поближе к нему. Но нет, он просто положил руку на спинку кресла и все."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:125
translate spanish hwb_s22b_639f66a4:

    # Marina "Like he was just stretching."
    Marina "Как будто бы он просто решил потянуться."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:127
translate spanish hwb_s22b_f06b303f:

    # "She giggles at the memory."
    "Ella ríe ante el recuerdo."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:129
translate spanish hwb_s22b_0ec6a9eb:

    # Marina "Honestly I’d forgotten all about that until now. That’s how not-a-real-boyfriend he was."
    Marina "Если честно, я вообще об этом уже забыла. Настолько “настоящим” парнем он был."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:133
translate spanish hwb_s22b_76aab332:

    # Marina "What about you?"
    Marina "А что на счет тебя?"

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:135
translate spanish hwb_s22b_2940a289:

    # "I’m glad that right now, things seem normal. Maybe if she’s talking, she forgets about being worried."
    "Me alegra que ahora las cosas parezcan normales. Quizás si habla, se olvida de estar preocupada."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:139
translate spanish hwb_s22b_f2918aae:

    # Amber "Well, I’ve never had a boyfriend."
    Amber "Ну, парня у меня никогда не было."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:141
translate spanish hwb_s22b_0f9e732a:

    # "Marina punches me in the shoulder."
    "Marina me da un puñetazo en el hombro."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:145
translate spanish hwb_s22b_e1b8f234:

    # Marina "You know what I meant! I could’ve guessed that much."
    Marina "Ты знаешь, что я имела в виду! Что у тебя не было парня, я и так смогла догадаться."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:149
translate spanish hwb_s22b_f1320f2b:

    # Amber "Hey now, I’m just being clear. But yeah, I’ve had other girlfriends."
    Amber "Хэй, я просто говорю на чистоту. Но да, у меня были другие девушки."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:151
translate spanish hwb_s22b_23781314:

    # "Isn’t it bad manners to talk about this? Especially early in a relationship?"
    "¿No es de mala educación hablar de esto? ¿Especialmente al principio de una relación?"

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:155
translate spanish hwb_s22b_58b63a25:

    # "She asked, though."
    "Pero ella preguntó."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:159
translate spanish hwb_s22b_a5d472d5:

    # Amber "They counted, though it wasn’t really anything serious either. By the time I was old enough for a serious relationship, I was too busy with taking care of Gramps to focus on one."
    Amber "Они считаются, хотя там не было ничего серьезного. К тому моменту, как я достаточно повзрослела для серьезных отношений, я была слишком занята ухаживая за дедушкой, чтобы найти время на них."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:163
translate spanish hwb_s22b_ae4d279d:

    # Amber "But at least no one’s mom ever told them they had to break up with me."
    Amber "Но, по крайней мере, ничья мать не говорила никому, что они должны со мной расстаться."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:167
translate spanish hwb_s22b_0f44a8bb:

    # Marina "Listen, it was hard when I was 12."
    Marina "Слушай, в мои 12 лет это было обидно."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:171
translate spanish hwb_s22b_8127ef78:

    # Marina "For like a day or two."
    Marina "На денек-другой."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:173
translate spanish hwb_s22b_acb5ced9:

    # Amber "I’ll bet."
    Amber "Не сомневаюсь!"

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:177
translate spanish hwb_s22b_c1a32fb7:

    # Amber "Anyway, yeah, there was this girl I was with through a chunk of high school. We broke up in… Junior year, I think? She wanted to focus on school."
    Amber "В любом случае, была одна с которой мы недолго встречались в старшей школе и расстались в первый же год... вроде бы. Она хотела сконцентрироваться на учебе."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:179
translate spanish hwb_s22b_73e8c1f6:

    # Amber "She ended up getting a full ride to a nice college, so I guess she made the right call."
    Amber "Кстати, потом она оказалась в очень неплохом колледже. Так что, похоже, она сделала правильный выбор."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:181
translate spanish hwb_s22b_aa53fda9:

    # "Marina doesn’t miss a beat."
    "Marina no pierde el ritmo."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:185
translate spanish hwb_s22b_e0e3c678:

    # Marina "Nah, it was her loss."
    Marina "Не, это был неправильный выбор."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:192
translate spanish hwb_s22b_f03762b7:

    # "I shift to free my arm that’s pressed against Marina’s side, and instead wrap it around her."
    "Me muevo para liberar mi brazo que está presionado contra el costado de Marina, y en su lugar lo enrollo alrededor de ella."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:196
translate spanish hwb_s22b_7cb2b10b:

    # "At first I can feel her tense up, but then she gradually relaxes, until most of her weight rests on me."
    "Al principio siento que se tensa, pero luego se relaja gradualmente, hasta que la mayor parte de su peso descansa sobre mí."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:200
translate spanish hwb_s22b_3091528f:

    # Marina "So Amber."
    Marina "Так что, Эмбер?"

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:204
translate spanish hwb_s22b_e23d32e8:

    # Amber "Hm?"
    Amber "М?"

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:208
translate spanish hwb_s22b_8621d102:

    # "She doesn’t answer."
    "Ella no responde."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:212
translate spanish hwb_s22b_aa3b3695:

    # Amber "Mare?"
    Amber "Мари?"

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:216
translate spanish hwb_s22b_5c4e835c:

    # Marina "Sorry, never mind."
    Marina "Не важно, прости."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:221
translate spanish hwb_s22b_9a7a7134:

    # "She looks up and smiles at me, and I smile back."
    "Levanta la vista y me sonríe, y yo le devuelvo la sonrisa."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:223
translate spanish hwb_s22b_8c863799:

    # "Maybe it’s better not to think too much right now, or ask too many questions."
    "Quizás sea mejor no pensar demasiado ahora, ni hacer demasiadas preguntas."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:225
translate spanish hwb_s22b_de401a1b:

    # "It’s just the two of us, being happy with each other. Not minding that we’re both sweaty and kind of gross right now, or that we haven’t eaten in hours."
    "Somos solo nosotras dos, siendo felices la una con la otra. Sin importar que ambas estemos sudadas y un poco asquerosas ahora, o que no hayamos comido en horas."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:227
translate spanish hwb_s22b_fecd8e3d:

    # "Or so I think."
    "O eso creo."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:229
translate spanish hwb_s22b_4c8c8d36:

    # "It isn’t long before she yawns, and looks up at me apologetically."
    "No pasa mucho tiempo antes de que bostece y me mire con aire de disculpa."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:233
translate spanish hwb_s22b_2c7546fa:

    # Marina "Whoops."
    Marina "Ой."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:237
translate spanish hwb_s22b_0b04b194:

    # Amber "It’s okay, I’m kind of tired too."
    Amber "Все в порядке, я тоже подустала."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:239
translate spanish hwb_s22b_875d7ae5:

    # "I’m not. I’m too excited still. But I don’t want her to feel bad about going to bed."
    "No lo estoy. Todavía estoy demasiado emocionada. Pero no quiero que se sienta mal por irse a dormir."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:241
translate spanish hwb_s22b_a65ec501:

    # "Plus, we did a lot of hiking today."
    "Además, caminamos mucho hoy."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:246
translate spanish hwb_s22b_1f437335:

    # "I unwind my arm from around her and switch which hand holds hers, so that we can stand up."
    "Desenredo mi brazo de alrededor de ella y cambio de mano para sostener la suya, para que podamos levantarnos."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:248
translate spanish hwb_s22b_1d2d7e8a:

    # "She’s fidgety again, shifting her weight from foot to foot."
    "Está inquieta de nuevo, cambiando su peso de un pie al otro."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:250
translate spanish hwb_s22b_470186de:

    # "Well, I guess it’ll take some getting used to. For both of us."
    "Bueno, supongo que tomará un tiempo acostumbrarse. Para ambas."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:252
translate spanish hwb_s22b_bff15f6e:

    # "I let go of her hand. It falls limply back to her side, like she lost control of it."
    "Suelto su mano. Cae flácida a su costado, como si hubiera perdido el control de ella."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:256
translate spanish hwb_s22b_6cbcbe9c:

    # "Looking me in the eye, I can tell she’s waiting for me to do or say something."
    "Mirándome a los ojos, puedo notar que espera que haga o diga algo."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:261
translate spanish hwb_s22b_12e10f1a:

    # "I take a step towards her, closing the short distance between us."
    "Doy un paso hacia ella, cerrando la corta distancia entre nosotras."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:263
translate spanish hwb_s22b_4a35b538:

    # Amber "Well, good night."
    Amber "Доброй ночи."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:265
translate spanish hwb_s22b_c96c5e09:

    # "And then I lean in and kiss her again."
    "Y entonces me inclino y la beso otra vez."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:272
translate spanish hwb_s22b_86cd710a:

    # "Briefly. Enough that she doesn’t even really have time to react before I pull away."
    "Brevemente. Lo suficiente para que ni siquiera tenga tiempo de reaccionar antes de que me aparte."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:274
translate spanish hwb_s22b_f0ff0eb6:

    # "She blinks twice, then rubs her lips and smiles."
    "Parpadea dos veces, luego se frota los labios y sonríe."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:278
translate spanish hwb_s22b_2a40fbc9:

    # Marina "Good night!"
    Marina "Доброй ночи!"

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:285
translate spanish hwb_s22b_b85583a9:

    # "She walks backwards away from me, still smiling. And I’m grinning like an idiot too, of course."
    "Camina hacia atrás alejándose de mí, aún sonriendo. Y yo también estoy sonriendo como una idiota, por supuesto."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:287
translate spanish hwb_s22b_be6a8c03:

    # "I’m tempted - so tempted - to invite her to sleep in my bed. Just to be close to her, still."
    "Estoy tentada —muy tentada— a invitarla a dormir en mi cama. Solo para estar cerca de ella, todavía."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:289
translate spanish hwb_s22b_74368f6d:

    # "But I don’t. Since she’s still so nervous and unsure, I don’t want to make that harder for her."
    "Pero no lo hago. Como todavía está tan nerviosa e insegura, no quiero hacerle las cosas más difíciles."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:295
translate spanish hwb_s22b_496668b9:

    # "I lick my lips as I go to turn off the lights, still tasting the sweetness of her on them."
    "Me lamo los labios mientras voy a apagar las luces, aún saboreando su dulzura en ellos."

# game/script/hwb_s22b.rpy:297
translate spanish hwb_s22b_10f71254:

    # "As I climb into bed, listening for the sounds of her breathing, I don’t expect to get much sleep of my own tonight."
    "Mientras me meto en la cama, escuchando los sonidos de su respiración, no espero dormir mucho esta noche."

translate spanish strings:

    # script/hwb_s22b.rpy:325
    old "Trying to sleep"
    new "Trying to sleep"

